Package org.jsonurl Description

This package provides an extensible JSON→URL parser core and static utility methods.

If you need a parser bound to your own JSON model API then a ValueFactory may be created and supplied to an instance of Parser. Otherwise, if a parser based on J2SE datatypes is sufficient then take a look at JsonUrlParser which does just that.

2019-09-01
